<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="83" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="83">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="83">
Prasanth and Jose published their findings in January 2014, whereas Sanap and Mirza published their discovery in July 2014, so priority must go to the name 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Haploclastus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Haploclastus devamatha" order="Araneae" pageId="2" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="devamatha">Haploclastus devamatha</taxonomicName>
and the name 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Thrigmopoeus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Thrigmopoeus psychedelicus" order="Araneae" pageId="2" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="psychedelicus">Thrigmopoeus psychedelicus</taxonomicName>
becomes its junior synonym.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
